original_title: Disney Parks Presents a Disney Channel Holiday Celebration
overview: The Raven-Symone and Issac Ryan Brown from Raven's Home take the stage as the hosts of the broadcast a rundown of the proceedings; musical performances from Disney Channel stars, a sneak peek at Disney's Hollywood Studios Toy Story Land, and surprise Disney experiences for families that "share the joy."
title: Disney Parks Presents a Disney Channel Holiday Celebration
